# Project Rules – Nuxt3 Blog (SSG)

## Architecture
- Static site with `nuxi generate`
- Pages: /, /about, /articles, /articles/:slug (Markdown via @nuxt/content)

## Coding Standards
- Use TypeScript and `<script setup lang="ts">`
- TailwindCSS only（no scoped CSS, avoid @apply）
- Composition API + Pinia for state

## Task Guidance
- Prefer Plan → Act モード
- 分割コミット必須（1タスク 1コミット）